transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello? Hello. Hello. Hello. Hi, good morning.
Customer: Good morning.
Executive: Tulsian Healthcare Private Limited baat ho rahi hai mam meri?
Customer: Yes sir, bataiye.
Executive: Aapka ticket aaya tha mere paas that Tulsian don't want to change his account manager so please connect and help them. To bataiye mam kya issue aa raha hai?
Customer: Sir matlab aap kis platform pe call kar rahe ho like Amazon ya issue?
Executive: No, no, I'm calling from IndiaMART, sorry.
Customer: Accha, you so ek minute main concern person ko deti hu. Main concern person ko deti hu.

Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello, yes.
Customer: Sir abhi concern person jaise aaye nahi hai to main aapko connect karu isi number pe connect karna hai?
Executive: Ha isi number pe karna hai aap isi number pe kaise nahi to main kar lunga thodi der baad fir agar.
Customer: Theek hai, theek hai. Theek hai, okay, thank you.
Executive: Thank you.
